{"tid":1442523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文宣JJ入）不要說Gear,full gear,試著說PPE","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:49:09.000Z","uid":275380,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1be04f9f7d9de005c5d875d9652edfd3ffc274","tid":1442523,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:44.000Z","msg":"發夢既時候因爲夢境像真度高，感覺到有風險及危害，配戴合適個人防護裝備（personal protective equipment),<br />\n係好適度既做法。<br />\n<br />\n而full gear 係感覺好型而勇悍，不過，<br />\n一，實際上都未算係full gear,<br />\n二，予人口實，藍屍癈老又放大黎講<br />\n<br />\n三，再下一步，要奴工處交待個人防護裝備既定性，作為前奴福局局長既張建宗都要回應下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f510fe89295e9d1a5c8064c7ed6faa2663a275b4","tid":1442523,"uid":60000,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"試講Pepe"},{"pid":"19cc5d4324be1169bd890eb534d9adc02938fc72","tid":1442523,"uid":275380,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f510fe89295e9d1a5c8064c7ed6faa2663a275b4","tid":1442523,"uid":60000,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:45:12.000Z","msg":"試講Pepe"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"係PPE呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa1f7195b7273b623b5b84af8012b4b22f62fbb","tid":1442523,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d4cea3b38cd27bd727f3613bd6660b1ccab225","tid":1442523,"uid":32464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"唔係睇全名都無咩人知PPE係咩<br />\n<br />\n一眼望落去以為唔知咩專業術語啲名，<br />\n普通人又聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 100人入面有1個人講記得個日要 PPE ，最後都唔知有無10個聽得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18c11308482af01b6a8ba6cb1e2dac12ac07741","tid":1442523,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"有什麼是抗爭者可做，但還未做的事？X先生說：「第一，我講多次，就係日日打721呢個死穴，因為林鄭同警方依家完全冇得拆。第二，將民建聯同黑警綑綁，要佢哋永不分離。中央撐警，建制派一定要歸隊，冇可能割席。好多人冇留意到北京撐警，其實係一把雙刃劍，好處係穩定軍心，防止警察叛變，壞處係會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。」<br />\n<br />\nBy 政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b3e3d4800da08139dcfdcdc5e6f9f40d9b10012","tid":1442523,"uid":114361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"PPE <br />\nGown up"},{"pid":"ac98821cb6d75ecf5935246a511861f951ba373c","tid":1442523,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.safetydirectory.hk/ebook/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.safetydirectory.hk%2Febook%2Findex.html&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=6e3fabd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.safetydirectory.hk/ebook/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"3f7d1a3d9aa65ee37f9d168e0f5e0c85021fafd2","tid":1442523,"uid":177047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"職安健呀，地盤尚且都要個人防護裝備"},{"pid":"d087880861c0e48109fd917b68a66b0ed62a6372","tid":1442523,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d4cea3b38cd27bd727f3613bd6660b1ccab225","tid":1442523,"uid":32464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"唔係睇全名都無咩人知PPE係咩<br />\n<br />\n一眼望落去以為唔知咩專業術語啲名，<br />\n普通人又聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 100人入面有1個人講記得個日要 PPE ，最後都唔知有無10個聽得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201